Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:23:02.46,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And so tender that I could crush it easily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:12.77,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never showed anyone any of my weaknesses till now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:18.96,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur3}I was able to endure any pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:24.93,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur3}But I didn't want to know this feeling
